        <div id="dsq-comment-body-1520" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-1520" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>I&#8217;m a long-time UNIX bigot but I&#8217;ll take SQL Server over Oracle any day.</p>
